óŔRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/encode_hex.mdŔ@6a85098ebdc316def01f37b002f238c2a7450f6b5e7a324833e6ea90b4d3e5b2Ītitle: encode hexĎ®ExamplesŕEncode a binary value
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[C3 06] | encode hex
C306

```
Encode a string
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "hello" | encode hex
68656C6C6F

```
Output a Lowercase version of the encoding
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[AD EF] | encode hex --lower
adef

```
